# .raw-exemptions/raw_7.list — grandfather list for raw#7 (F1/F2/F3/F5/F6)
# format: <file_path> | <line_range> | <reason> | <expiry YYYY-MM-DD>
# expiry REQUIRED — indefinite grandfather forbidden.
#
# Scanner consultation status (2026-04-26):
#   F4  via raw_6.list                       — ENFORCED
#   F1/F2/F3/F5/F6  via raw_7.list           — CONTRACTUAL (scanner emits
#       residual-highlights; see config/launchd/com.anima.lint_cron.plist
#       for daily delta tracking → state/lint_cron_history.jsonl)
#
# All entries 12-month review (expiry 2027-04-26). jurisdiction-out tag
# documents the structural boundary that puts the path outside F1-F6 scope.
# owner = anima for every entry.

